description: This big baby blue truck is serving the streets of Orange County a deliciously refreshing selection of frozen yogurt treats!You’ll find delightfully creamy frozen yogurt in all sorts of wonderful flavors that include Chocolate Caramel Turtle, New York Cheesecake, Mango Tango Sorbet, just to name a few. Feel free to top your treat with tasty options like fresh fruit, marshmallows, peanut butter cups, almonds, and many more!For flavorful fun you’re sure to love, come on over to We Heart Froyo!
name: We Heart Froyo
